      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is an absolute gem\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays in pristine shape. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for an adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Come see it for yourself, you're going to love it!",
