    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen exhibits exceptional mechanical health, with recent shim-and-bucket valve adjustments and proactive rod bearing replacement documented. The chassis is structurally immaculate, benefiting from rear subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. The exterior retains its original Carbon Black Metallic finish with zero orange peel or swirl marks, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather with firm bolsters and fully functional electronics. Every aspect of the dual-VANOS system and the variable M-differential lock functions with factory precision, making this an investment-grade example of the ultimate driving machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Pristine condition. No mechanical issues. Clean title. Single owner. Non-smoker. Full service records available.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
