    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, preserved in a state that rivals its original debut on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and kept strictly in a climate-controlled environment. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather still retains its factory scent, and every surface\u2014from the dashboard to the door cards\u2014is free of wear, scuffing, or UV fading. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive, meticulously documented service history from day one. It drives exactly as it did when new, offering a tight, responsive experience with no rattles, hesitations, or mechanical flaws. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly flawless example of automotive excellence that has been treated with the utmost care.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
